name: Fluidity
description: I did this piece for Orphan Crypto‘s Thunderdome. The timed them was meditation and water. In a nutshell, the concept is about the importance of dealing with all the garbage that enters our system, spiritually and emotionally. There is a need to allow it to process and flow out of us. I made this piece in a parking lot on my hour lunch break, there’s a lot I don’t like about it, but some things I do. I love making pixel art, and so for HEN10k, I give this to you with all its imperfections. Unsold copies except 1 will be burned by Monday, June 21st 2021.
